2/ MYTH: Air travel danger eliminated post-9/11 w/ TSA. REALITY: Huge false positive (bag gets pulled aside) and false negative (dangerous objects get through) counts. @SynTechCorp is building comp vision and ML technology to aid humans in evaluating threats in real time.
